		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Hypothetical: Your Dream IP to license</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />For the sake of conversation, let's say you (had the opportunity / were obligated) to create a title for the NES using a previously existing intellectual property. You have free reign in terms of creative control and cost to acquire said license is not a factor.<br /><br />What property would you want to use and why?<br />What type of game would you make?<br />How would you incorporate the license into the game?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


