		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well that's mainly speaking of using the Alien(s) IP. It'd be quite fun to try to copy the visual style of the movie and make it a game. The architetcure, dominant colours, the hazy, fedback feed on their monitors, etc. The synopsis for the design in itself might be worth revisiting sometime perhaps and try to make better. <br /><br />Maybe a point and click adventure or limited sandbox featuring <a href="https://www.moomin.com/en/" class="postlink">Moomin</a>, then. It's such a lush, dynamic world and i don't think moomin fans have ever been able to explore it themselves in that way. When i read the Moomin books and graphic novels as a kid, all i wanted was to go there myself and invent my own adventure.

		

		</td>
